column5: Managed to get out this morning on cooks, man has it ever gotten cold in the mornings... Scored this nice 30 incher at about 8:30  Leaving tomorrow for Marten River North Bay for our honeymoon for a week! hope to get lots of big pike!
congrats on the pike...oh ya, and on the marriage! So did you get out on Cooks Bay the day you got married?
Do you think I'd be able to type if I did that?
Love the bay. Cottage in Belle Ewart many fish caught in that bay!
